c: 28
v: 45
t: "Ahubwo twaremye ibisekuru byinshi (nyuma ya Musa), bibaho igihe kirekire [(biza kwibagirwa isezerano rya Allah, kugeza ubwo uje (Muhamadi)], kandi nta n’ubwo wabaye mu bantu b’i Madiyana ngo ubasomere amagambo yacu. Ariko ni twe twoherezaga (intumwa, tukanaziha inkuru z’ibyabaye mbere)"